对地区进行处理，把它分成城市、城区和街道三个部分并保存到数据中¶

In [5]:
boss['城市']=[i.split('·')[0] for i in boss.地区]
boss['城区']='null'
boss['街道']='null'
for i in boss['地区'].index:
    try:
        boss['城区'][i]=boss['地区'][i].split('·')[1]
        boss['街道'][i]=boss['地区'][i].split('·')[2]
    except:
        boss['城区'][i]='nan'
        boss['街道'][i]='nan'

对薪资进行处理，保留去除年终奖的部分，并转换成统一的每个月工资¶

In [6]:
for i in boss['薪资'].index:
    try:
        boss['薪资'][i]=boss['薪资'][i].split('·')[0]
    except:
        pass
for i in boss['薪资'].index:
    if 'K' in boss['薪资'][i]:
        min=boss['薪资'][i].replace('K','').split('-')[0]
        max=boss['薪资'][i].replace('K','').split('-')[1]
        boss['薪资'][i]=((int(min)*1000)+(int(max)*1000))/2
    elif '元/天' in boss['薪资'][i]:
        try:
            min=boss['薪资'][i].replace('元/天','').split('-')[0]
            max=boss['薪资'][i].replace('元/天','').split('-')[1]
            boss['薪资'][i]=((int(min)+int(max))/2)*30
        except:
            max=boss['薪资'][i].replace('元/天','')
            boss['薪资'][i]=float(max)*30
    elif '元/时' in boss['薪资'][i]:
        min=boss['薪资'][i].replace('元/时','').split('-')[0]
        max=boss['薪资'][i].replace('元/时','').split('-')[1]
        boss['薪资'][i]=(((int(min)*8)+(int(max)*8))/2)*30
    elif '元/月' in boss['薪资'][i]:
        min=boss['薪资'][i].replace('元/月','').split('-')[0]
        max=boss['薪资'][i].replace('元/月','').split('-')[1]
        boss['薪资'][i]=(int(min)+int(max))/2

        words=words+boss['福利'][i].split('，')

        pass
In [89]:
word_count = {}
for word in words:
    if word not in word_count:
        word_count[word] = 1
    else:
        word_count[word] += 1
In [93]:

)
